{"tid":812087,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓再現MERS確診個案 20人被隔離","createTime":"2018-09-09T11:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T12:31:25.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1e6ad9e6940d00ac4e6a79028e5b7dceb0da412c","tid":812087,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:15:31.000Z","msg":"南韓再現MERS確診個案 20人被隔離<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201809080262-1.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F201809080262-1.aspx&d=UYZM1tQsFbWjGLhbwLF%2BfhFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=187995a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201809080262-1.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n（中央社記者姜遠珍首爾8日專電）南韓今天宣布，一名61歲南韓男性被確診為中東呼吸症候群冠狀病毒感染症（MERS-CoV），與他接觸過的20人已被隔離。這是自2015年後，南韓再次出現MERS-CoV確診個案。<br />\n<br />\n南韓KBS電視台以速報字幕報導指出，這名患者於今年8月16日至9月6日因出差而停留在科威特，7日經由阿拉伯聯合大公國杜拜返回首爾。<br />\n<br />\n南韓疾病管理本部透露，這名患者8月28日因腹瀉曾在科威特當地醫院接受治療，其後一直有腹瀉症狀，返國後由機場直接送往三星首爾醫院急診室。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，三星首爾醫院將這名患者送進急診室的隔離病室後，發現他一直呈現發燒、咳痰及肺炎症狀，於是向政府保健當局申報疑似中東呼吸症候群冠狀病毒感染症個案，並將他轉送到有國家隔離指定病床的國立首爾大學附屬醫院。<br />\n<br />\n首爾市保健環境研究院檢驗患者的檢體後，確認他是中東呼吸症候群冠狀病毒感染症患者。<br />\n<br />\n南韓疾病管理本部與首爾市已針對這名患者搭乘的客機、接受治療的醫院等與患者有過接觸的人逐一展開檢驗，目前已對1名檢驗官、1名機場移民署官員、3名客機空服人員、10名同機乘客、4名醫療人員、1名家屬等20人採取隔離措施。<br />\n<br />\n2015年5月20日南韓公布首例中東呼吸症候群冠狀病毒感染症個案後，至同年12月23日韓國官方宣布疫情正式結束，被隔離的人數多達1萬6752人，共有186人感染疫情，其中有38人喪生。（編輯：施燕飛）1070908"},{"pid":"b2a0990fc846df6b4cb2912b82756244a6dae34f","tid":812087,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9fce14ce1678f1b587f025467cb02a945cc9e3","tid":812087,"uid":17896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:53:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://goo.gl/images/azSHVB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fimages%2FazSHVB&d=UYZM1tQsFbWjGLhbwLF%2BfhFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=36f5b923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/images/azSHVB</a>"},{"pid":"2a31fb2e48e4133ac7e5190a495701f4628c8d35","tid":812087,"uid":115268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:56:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=9DeC5jGNVVs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9DeC5jGNVVs&d=UYZM1tQsFbWjGLhbwLF%2BfhFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=f56147de\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=9DeC5jGNVVs</a> 又要loop呢一段"},{"pid":"754c5ca98044d0d775c6a0f3ffccaccaaf830cc9","tid":812087,"uid":49549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T11:59:29.000Z","msg":"好快個阿個同20個人又會走出黎1"},{"pid":"a5a2e4917b381b3297483f7e49022600cda53d29","tid":812087,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T12:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}